title: Douglas Adams & The Hitchhikers Guide to the Galaxy
description:
Douglas Adams 'Don't Panic' or 'The Hitchhikers Guide to the Galaxy'.
Included are Audiobooks, PDF & LIT Books, Infocom Game (links & walkthrough), the 2005 Movie, the Primary & Secondary & Tertiary & Quintessential Radio Series (including theme tracks, and some radio scripts) as well as 'Douglas Adams at the BBC' and the 1978 HHGTTG, and (finally) the 1981 TV Series.

Audiobooks in MP3 format - 56-80kps mono/stereo
Movie in MP4 format - Video 720p@1100kbps - Audio 48K@160kps Stereo
Radio in MP3 format - 56-256kps stereo
TV Series in MP4 format - Video 720p@1500kbps - Audio 48K@128kps Stereo

- Covers included -
